{"tid":1583990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門站一時起關閉 元朗站三時關閉","createTime":"2019-09-21T02:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T02:15:32.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"da4949f31215bcf72de2399b2d3404a983fc31aa","tid":1583990,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T02:06:24.000Z","msg":"此訊息發放時間 : 2019-09-21 10:00<br />\n<br />\n列車服務延誤/受阻 &ndash; 東鐵綫<br />\n由於有公眾活動進行，經風險評估及與相關政府部門商討後，為審慎起見，西鐵綫列車服務會於稍後時間作出調整，以保障乘客及員工的安全：<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 由下午一時起，屯門站暫時關閉，列車不停屯門站<br />\n&bull; 由下午三時起，元朗站暫時關閉，列車不停元朗站<br />\n<br />\n同樣基於安全考慮，其他車站或其部份出入口可能會隨時關閉，而未能預早通知。<br />\n<br />\n請預早計劃行程，感謝您的體諒。"},{"pid":"78af0bb13ad6f32b5ab4deb2bf976ed547b5e429","tid":1583990,"uid":90012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T02:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sfb9TDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSfb9TDQ.jpg&h=9d815f72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bXnJdDR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbXnJdDR.jpg&h=d271e787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MxBByDS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMxBByDS.jpg&h=43fd1da6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fe334b2e1075d8b52c379bc173394cd3b8a5c62","tid":1583990,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T02:08:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"477b33c0daf6810d01c54b1c675d821db42378d8","tid":1583990,"uid":237555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T02:11:13.000Z","msg":"沙田反而唔封？"},{"pid":"ebba356a8b42df2c54e148ba59981ca62082f093","tid":1583990,